HEADWORD: Inkstand
<hw>Ink"stand`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A small vessel for
holding ink, to dip the pen into; also, a device for holding ink and
writing materials.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

